Chelsea Field https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chelsea_Field 0 Chelsea Field (born May 27, 1957) is an American actress. She played Teela in the 1987 film adaptation of Masters of the Universe. Field started her career as a dancer with her first TV role on Airwolf. She appeared opposite her husband in several episodes of season four of NCIS: New Orleans.
